  const int i = (lvap_ > 0) + (hls_ > 0) + (hvs_ > 0);

  if (lvap_ > 0 && hls_ > 0) hvs_ = hls_ + lvap_;
  else if (lvap_ > 0 && hvs_ > 0) hls_ = hvs_ - lvap_;
  else if (hls_ > 0 && hvs_ > 0) lvap_ = hvs_ - hls_;
  else Process::exit(que_suis_je() + "bad parameters");
  return is;
